  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/11/bing-bitcoin-conversion-tool/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/ac5fb66ffe5e29115f1ca6dbf30703fa/bingcoin.png\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/bitcoin\">比特币</a>在某些地方的发展受到了<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/10/russian-authorities-reject-bitcoin/\">阻碍</a>，但其在网络上的影响力的确在变得越来越大。<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/bing\">Bing</a> 与 Coinbase 间最新的合作就是个很好的例子，从今天开始，前者将在自己的搜索引擎中加入比特币换算功能，方便用户计算自己手头虚拟货币的价值（支持 50 多种现实货币换算）。怎么样？挖到现在去算算总共赚了多少吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/02/10/bing-bitcoin-conversion-tool/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://recode.net/2014/02/10/bing-unveils-bitcoin-currency-conversion-with-help-of-coinbase/\" target=\"_blank\">re/code</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.bing.com/blogs/site_blogs/b/search/archive/2014/02/10/coinbit.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Bing</a></span><br />\n更多信息：<span class=\"more-coverage\"><a href=\"http://blog.coinbase.com/post/76234094435/microsoft-bing-and-coinbase-make-real-time-bitcoin\" target=\"_blank\">Coinbase</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/11/bing-bitcoin-conversion-tool/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20827250/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/02/11/bing-bitcoin-conversion-tool/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
